item.title: Baba Yetu
item.description: Baba yetu yetu’uliye mbinguni yetu yetu amina. Baba yetu yetu’uliye mjina lako elitukuzwe. Utupe leo chakula chetu tunachohitaji. Utusamehe makosa yetu, hey! Kama nasi tunavyowasamehe waliotukosea. Usitutie katika majaribu, lakini utuokoe na yule, | muovu e milele!| Baba yetu yetu’uliye mbinguni yetu yetu amina. Baba yetu yetu’uliye mjina lako elitukuzwe. Ufalme wako ufike utakalo lifanyike duniani kama mbinguni. Amina Baba yetu yetu’uliye mbinguni yetu yetu amina. Baba yetu yetu’uliye mjina lako elitukuzwe.
